Command> gh pr checkout

Arguments> [issue number|branch] [flags]

TL;DR> checkout a pull request

Keywords> github
        > pull_request

Description>
           > -b, --branch
           >    local branch name to use
           >
           > --detach
           >    checkout pr with a detached HEAD
           >
           > -f, --force
           >
           > --recurse-submodules
           >
           >


Reference> https://cli.github.com/manual/gh_pr_checkout
